description: Windows host dashboard for telegraf metrics pumped into influxdb

targets.query: SELECT mean("Value") as PCH FROM "Sensor" WHERE ("Name"::tag = 'PCH') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host fill(linear) ORDER BY asc
SELECT mean("Value") as CPU FROM "Sensor" WHERE ("Name"::tag = 'CPU') AND host =~ /$hostname$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host fill(linear) ORDER BY asc
SELECT mean("Value") as System FROM "Sensor" WHERE ("Name"::tag = 'System') AND host =~ /$hostname$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host fill(linear) ORDER BY asc
SELECT mean("Value") as "VRM MOS" FROM "Sensor" WHERE ("Name"::tag = 'VRM MOS') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host fill(linear) ORDER BY asc
SELECT mean("Value") as PCIe FROM "Sensor" WHERE ("Name"::tag = 'PCIe x1') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host fill(linear) ORDER BY asc
SELECT mean("Value") as "CPU Socket" FROM "Sensor" WHERE ("Name"::tag = 'CPU Socket') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host fill(linear) ORDER BY asc
SELECT mean("Value") as M2 FROM "Sensor" WHERE ("Name"::tag = 'M2_1') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host fill(linear) ORDER BY asc
SELECT mean("Value") as "GPU Hot Spot" FROM "Sensor" WHERE  ("Name"::tag = 'GPU Hot Spot') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host fill(linear) ORDER BY asc
SELECT mean("Value") as "GPU Core" FROM "Sensor" WHERE ("Name"::tag = 'GPU Core' ) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host fill(linear) ORDER BY asc
SELECT mean("Value") as "Temp Core Max" FROM "Sensor" WHERE ("Name"::tag = 'Core Max') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host fill(linear) ORDER BY asc

SELECT mean("Available_Bytes") as "Available Bytes", mean("Pool_Nonpaged_Bytes") as "Pool Nonpaged Bytes", mean("Pool_Paged_Bytes") as "Pool Paged Bytes" FROM "win_mem" WHERE host =~ /$hostname$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host fill(linear) ORDER BY asc

SELECT mean("Percent_Privileged_Time") AS "% Priviledged Time", mean("Percent_User_Time") AS "% User Time", mean("Percent_Interrupt_Time") AS "% Interrupt Time", mean("Percent_Processor_Time") AS "% Processor Time" FROM "win_cpu" WHERE ("host" =~ /^$hostname$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(linear)
SELECT mean("Value") as "GPU Package" FROM "Sensor" WHERE ("Name"::tag = 'GPU Package') AND host =~ /$hostname$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host fill(linear) ORDER BY asc
SELECT mean("Value") as "CPU package power" FROM "Sensor" WHERE ("Name"::tag = 'CPU Package') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host fill(linear) ORDER BY asc

SELECT mean("Percent_Privileged_Time") AS "% Priviledged Time", mean("Percent_User_Time") AS "% User Time", mean("Percent_Interrupt_Time") AS "% Interrupt Time", mean("Percent_Processor_Time") AS "% Processor Time" FROM "win_cpu" WHERE ("host" =~ /^$hostname$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(linear)
SELECT mean("Value") as "Mémoire GPU dédié" FROM "Sensor" WHERE ("Name"::tag = 'D3D Dedicated Memory Used') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host fill(linear) ORDER BY asc

SELECT mean("Available_Bytes") as "Available Bytes", mean("Pool_Nonpaged_Bytes") as "Pool Nonpaged Bytes", mean("Pool_Paged_Bytes") as "Pool Paged Bytes" FROM "win_mem" WHERE host =~ /$hostname$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), host fill(linear) ORDER BY asc
